               <history>
                  <origin>
                     <origDate notBefore="1600" notAfter="1699">17th century</origDate>
                  </origin>
                  <provenance>There are numerous supplications for <persName ref="PRS15404TabdanaKr"
                     />, <persName ref="PRS15403GabraM"/>, <persName ref="PRS15402TasfaM"/> and
                     probably some more men. While <persName ref="PRS15404TabdanaKr"/> and <persName
                        ref="PRS15402TasfaM"/> seem to be original supplicants, the name of
                        <persName ref="PRS15403GabraM"/> was likely added later.</provenance>
               </history>
